Themes Engine Changelog
=======================
v0.0.4
------

- themes.gemspec update
- Add test coverage

v0.0.3
------

- Add generator to create new themes
- Let theme configuration file to load per environment configurations

v0.0.2
-------

- Load path for themed views under views/themes/THEME_NAME. It applies to controllers and mailers.

v0.0.1
-------

- Mailers default from set to theme configured email
- Allow app to load diferent configuration depending on theme
- Load theme using APP_THEME environment variable

